window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A single drunken night changed everything.</p> <p>One positive test later, and I’m not only pregnant with my best friend’s baby, but I’m falling for him too.</p> <p>Except when my ex finds out at work, I do the worst thing I could at that moment: I lie.</p> <p>I make up a fake fiancé and my boss overhears.</p> <p>Now I need my best friend to play the part. He’s good at it, too, since we can’t keep our hands off each other.</p> <p>When we’re both forced to lean on each other, we’ll have to face facts.</p> <p>There’s nothing fake about this relationship.</p> <p>Even if I’ll break my heart in the process.</p>"; 
